import React from 'react';
import { Button, Form, FormGroup, Label, Input } from 'reactstrap';

const Example = (props) => {
  return (
    <Form>
      <FormGroup>
        <Label for="examplefirstName">First Name</Label>
        <Input type="firstName" name="firstName" id="examplefirstName" placeholder="John" />
      </FormGroup>

      <FormGroup>
        <Label for="examplelasttName">Last Name</Label>
        <Input type="lastName" name="lastName" id="examplelasttName" placeholder="Doe" />
      </FormGroup>

      <FormGroup>
        <Label for="exampleAge">Age</Label>
        <Input type="age" name="age" id="exampleAge" placeholder="23" />
      </FormGroup>

      <FormGroup>
        <Label for="exampleDOF">Date Of Birth</Label>
        <Input type="dob" name="dob" id="exampleDOF" placeholder="23" />
      </FormGroup>

      <FormGroup>
        <Label for="examplePassword">Password</Label>
        <Input type="password" name="password" id="examplePassword" placeholder="password placeholder" />
      </FormGroup>
  
      <Button>Submit</Button>
    </Form>
  );
}

export default Example;
